        "text": "From the moment we met Abie, we knew we were in good hands.\n\nHer talent behind the camera is undeniable. The photos she captured are full of heart, movement, and emotion. They tell the story of our wedding in a way that feels both honest and magical.\n\nBut what really made Abie stand out was the way she supported us throughout the whole weekend. She wasn’t just documenting moments. She was helping create calm, guiding the timeline, and making sure we were able to actually enjoy everything as it unfolded.\n\nHaving her there felt like having a close friend who just happened to be a world-class photographer. She brought warmth, steadiness, and joy to the entire experience.\n\nI can’t imagine the day without her - and I wouldn’t want to."
      },
