      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-01",
        "text": "We are so grateful to have had Abie photograph our wedding day! She did such an amazing job capturing the joy and beauty of the day which allowed us to enjoy every moment. She was great to work with during the planning process and a joy to have around on our day. The photos are absolutely unreal and more than we every could have dreamed of! We would highly recommend working with Abie and her team for any special event!"
