        "text": "We are endlessly grateful for Abie and the way she captured our elopement. From the moment she arrived, she brought such an uplifting, joyful presence that allowed us to simply be in the moment together. She spent four hours with us, documenting every laugh, kiss, and quiet glance with such intention and artistry. She was incredibly patient and loving with our 16-month-old daughter, making it possible for me to fully relax and soak in every bit of the day. The photos she delivered are pure magic, timeless, emotional, and full of warmth. Looking through them feels like reliving the day all over again. Abie truly has a gift for telling love stories, and we feel so lucky that she told ours."
